<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>수배업체 로그인 - 괌세이브카드</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .login-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .login-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .login-body {
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .form-control {
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            padding: 12px 15px;
        }
        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: #667eea;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.25);
        }
        .btn-login {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .btn-login:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }
        .alert {
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: none;
        }
        .assignment-info {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-5">
                <div class="login-card">
                    <div class="login-header">
                        <h3 class="mb-0">
                            <i class="bi bi-shield-lock me-2"></i>
                            수배업체 로그인
                        </h3>
                        <p class="mb-0 mt-2 opacity-75">수배서 확인을 위해 로그인해주세요</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="login-body">
                        <% if (assignmentInfo) { %>
                        <div class="assignment-info">
                            <h6 class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-file-text me-2"></i>수배서 정보</h6>
                            <div class="small">
                                <div><strong>예약번호:</strong> <%= assignmentInfo.reservation_number %></div>
                                <div><strong>상품명:</strong> <%= assignmentInfo.product_name %></div>
                                <div><strong>사용일자:</strong> <%= assignmentInfo.usage_date %></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <% } %>
                        
                        <% if (error) { %>
                        <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
                            <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>
                            <%= error %>
                        </div>
                        <% } %>
                        
                        <form action="/vendor/login" method="POST">
                            <input type="hidden" name="token" value="<%= token %>">
                            <input type="hidden" name="redirect" value="/assignment/<%= token %>">
                            
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="vendor_id" class="form-label">
                                    <i class="bi bi-person me-2"></i>수배업체 ID
                                </label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="vendor_id" name="vendor_id" 
                                       placeholder="수배업체 ID를 입력하세요" required autofocus>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="mb-4">
                                <label for="password" class="form-label">
                                    <i class="bi bi-lock me-2"></i>패스워드
                                </label>
                                <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" name="password" 
                                       placeholder="패스워드를 입력하세요" required>
                            </div>
                            
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-login w-100">
                                <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right me-2"></i>
                                수배서 확인하기
                            </button>
                        </form>
                        
                        <div class="text-center mt-4">
                            <small class="text-muted">
                                <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-1"></i>
                                수배업체 계정 정보는 괌세이브카드에서 제공됩니다
                            </small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
